info.author: Parker
info.description:
MVC Web Application Framework with Tornado, Python 2 and 3

To install the package run:

    pip install dp-tornado


Run
-----

    $ pip install virtualenv
    $ virtualenv ./venv
    $ . ./venv/bin/activate
    $ pip install dp-tornado
    $ dp4p init --path app
